static void cs_control(uint8_t op) {
    // Invert the logic - CS is typically active low
    gpio_set_pin_value(DISPLAY_CS_PIN_NAME, DISPLAY_CS_PIN_NUM, op == SSP_CS_ENABLE ? 0 : 1);
